Kamunuza ya Gikirisitu y u Rwanda " Christian university of Rwanda (CHUR) ni  kaminuza yigenga ikorera mu gihugu cy u Rwanda Ikaba itanga ubumenye mu mashami atandukanye ikaba ifite abanyeshure bari hagati (10,000-50,000) , ikaba iherereye mu ntara ya amajyaruguru mu mujyi wa gitesi<ref>https://igihe.com/amakuru/u-rwanda/article/abakozi-n-abanyeshuri-ba-christian-university-of-rwanda-basuye-urwibutso-rwa</ref> .


== AMATEKA ==


CHUR ni kamunuza nigenga y itorero ry abangirikani ikaba iri kumwanya wa 18 muri kamunuza zo mu Rwanda ikaba iri ku mwanya wa 12811 ku rutonde rwa kaminuza zo ku isi ,<ref>Christian University of Rwanda Ranking (topuniversitieslist.com)</ref>

== IMIYOBORERE ==
CHUR ifite ubuyobozi bwa akaminuza muri rusange bufatanya nu ubwabanyeshuri mu kugera ku iterambere rya kaminuza  

== ''AMASOMO'' ==
CHUR ifite amasomo atandukanye arimo , aya za siyanse na tekinologi , ubuhinzi ,iterambere  ry icyaro , uburezi na andi abanyeshuri ba CHUR bavomamo ubumenyi butandukanye <ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/uburezi/amashuri/article/mineduc-yatangaje-izindi-kaminuza-ebyiri-zahagaritswe</ref>

* Faculty of Science and Technology

* Faculty of Agriculture and Rural Development

* Faculty of Business, Trade and Investment

* Faculty of Education

* Faculty of Arts, Humanities and Social Sciences<ref>https://udahiliportal.com/christian-university-of-rwanda-chur-faculties</ref>

== Ibindi wamenya kuri CHUR ==
CHUR ni kaminuza yi genda ya gikiristu ya korega mu [[Rwanda]] ubu ikaba yarahagaritwe  mu mwaka wa 2020 muri kaminuza zitanga ubumenyi mu gihugu cy u Rwanda<ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/uburezi/amashuri/article/hec-siyo-ifunga-amashuri-ahubwo-nitwe-tubyitera-dr-habumuremye-damien</ref>  . 



